## Compilation & Execution

### Prerequisites
A compiler supporting standard C99 (GCC or Clang) is required.

### 1. Compile on Linux using Makefile
Run `make` in the repository root:
```bash
make
```

### 2. Manual Compile
```bash
gcc -Wall -Wextra -std=c99 -Iinclude src/graphics_editor.c -o graphics_editor -lm
```

### 3. Running the App
```bash
./graphics_editor
```

### 4. Cleaning Build Objects
```bash
make clean
```

